{"tid":962083,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾球員賤種朗 真正垃圾實力update 20181230","createTime":"2018-12-30T15:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T09:25:40.000Z","uid":54373,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8928bace8c9bb2b0786cdb906e02af1b001d11b9","tid":962083,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:05:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2018已完如,咪又係究比美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾朗又要靠12碼先識入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#數據post目的係唔想班賤朗迷再呃人<br />\n#上述數據由今季第1場比賽開始計算<br />\n#上述數據根據 who scored + 7m 賽後數據 每場累積而來<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賤種朗<br />\n聯賽: 125射14入球 (4球靠12碼) (11.2%)<br />\n歐聯: 27射1入球 1紅牌 (3.7%)<br />\n已射152球 得個15個入球 合共9.8%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯<br />\n聯賽: 71射15入球 (1球靠12碼) (21.1%)<br />\n歐聯: 20射6入球 0紅牌 (30%)<br />\n91射入21球 合共23%"},{"pid":"ad5493ac0b9607fd3babbf472ebd199037b15743","tid":962083,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:06:29.000Z","msg":"賤種朗<br />\n聯賽: 125射14入球 (4球靠12碼) (11.2%)<br />\n歐聯: 27射1入球 1紅牌 (3.7%)<br />\n已射152球 得個15個入球 合共9.8%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯<br />\n聯賽: 78射16入球 (1球靠12碼) (20.5%)<br />\n歐聯: 20射6入球 0紅牌 (30%)<br />\n98射入22球 合共22.2%"},{"pid":"d148883ff44a555eb8f47965cedfe4330f6c7bb8","tid":962083,"uid"